# Edge-case categories

| # | Category | Examples |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Empty/null | `[]`, `None`, `""` |
| 2 | Boundary numbers | 0, 1, max, max+1 |
| 3 | Off-by-one | last index, first index |
| 4 | Unicode | non-ASCII, emoji, RTL |
| 5 | Encoding | UTF-8, Latin-1, malformed |
| 6 | Time | leap second, DST, clock skew |
| 7 | Timezone | UTC vs local, ambiguous |
| 8 | Locale | decimal separator, sorting |
| 9 | Float | NaN, Inf, precision |
| 10 | Strings | whitespace, case, very long |
| 11 | Concurrency | race, deadlock, timeout |
| 12 | Resource | OOM, disk full, fd limit |
| 13 | Idempotency | duplicate calls |
| 14 | Adversarial | injection, oversized input |
